overview: Kelly arrives home and tries to slip into the house, but her step-father rushes into the room from elsewhere in the home and says, "There you are! I was worried sick!" He proceeds to lecture her, and as he does she starts to squirm nervously in place until she can't hold it any more. The first sign of a wet spot appears on her crotch which then trickles down her pant leg.
title: Daughter's Little Accident
